Apple Watch goes on display in stores this Friday in the US, UK, Australia, Canada, Hong Kong and Japan . 
  Any employee working in the regions where the watch is being launched will be eligible for a 50% discount on the standard model and the Sport model . 
  The discount does not apply to the Edition model which starts at $10,000 . 
  Apple Watch hits stores on 10 April and customers can pre-order it . 
  It will go on sale in general on 24 April in US and UK . 
 